[4] Iowa (Scott county)
Date: Mon 27 Feb 2012
Source: The Associated Press (AP) [summ., edited]
http://www.news8000.com/news/Eastern-Iowa-officials-warn-of-whooping-cough/-/326/9137536/-/5hcfuu/-/


The Scott County Health Department in eastern Iowa is sending out an alert that there are more whooping cough cases in area schools. Davenport television station KWQC reports that 10 cases were reported last week [week of 20 Feb 2012] alone.

Iowa has seen a jump in whooping cough cases in recent years.

